OVER LAST 2 YEARS WITH THE LAST UNIT BEING THE REFRIGERATOR 6 WEEKS AGO. Welcome Home to this beautiful cozy renovated house that is move-in ready. This home sits on a corner lot with a view that you don't see everyday. Enter in and you'll be greeted with hard-wood floor that runs throughout the home. First, you'll find the living/dining rooms that flows right into the lovely kitchen. This layout allows you to prepare your meals whilst, watching the kids play or just simple having a conversation with friends and families. The lovely bay window in the living room (with newly added shutters) flood these rooms with a ton of natural light.  This floor is completed with 3 bedrooms and a lovely, lovely lovely bathroom and storage is not an issue.  The stairs takes you to the lower level  with also a fully renovated bathroom and a massive space just waiting for you to convert it to just about anything you so desire. On this level you'll also find the laundry area. Want to relax? Take a step out to the fully fenced backyard. YOUR OWN SANCTUARY. Lovely well-manicured lawn awaiting those family/friends gatherings where you'll create those priceless moments. What are you waiting for, come and take a look!  Pending Release ..
